    <h3 class="heading-medium" id="document-downloads">Document downloads</h3>

    <div class="panel panel-border-wide text">
      <p>I&rsquo;ve opted for a non CSS3 Box Shadow approach to ensure consistent look and feel across all browsers.</p>
